Package sealey.javafxinventorysystem

Class ModifyProduct

java.lang.Object
sealey.javafxinventorysystem.ModifyProduct
All Implemented Interfaces:
javafx.fxml.Initializable
public class ModifyProduct extends Object implements javafx.fxml.Initializable
The ModifyProduct controller controls the components used to edit the values and associated parts of the selected product.
Author:
Max Sealey
